1
00:01:12,072 --> 00:01:13,949
SURAK.

2
00:01:18,078 --> 00:01:20,539
♪ IT'S BEEN A LONG ROAD ♪

3
00:01:20,539 --> 00:01:23,667
♪ GETTING FROM THERE TO HERE ♪

4
00:01:23,667 --> 00:01:27,629
♪ IT'S BEEN A LONG TIME ♪

5
00:01:27,629 --> 00:01:31,341
♪ BUT MY TIME IS FINALLY NEAR ♪

6
00:01:31,341 --> 00:01:35,930
♪ AND I WILL SEE MY DREAM
COME ALIVE AT LAST ♪

7
00:01:35,930 --> 00:01:39,391
♪ I WILL TOUCH THE SKY ♪

8
00:01:39,391 --> 00:01:43,102
♪ AND THEY'RE NOT GONNA
HOLD ME DOWN NO MORE ♪

9
00:01:43,102 --> 00:01:46,023
♪ NO, THEY'RE NOT GONNA
CHANGE MY MIND ♪

10
00:01:46,023 --> 00:01:48,859
♪ 'CAUSE I'VE GOT FAITH ♪

11
00:01:48,859 --> 00:01:50,986
♪ OF THE HEART ♪

12
00:01:50,986 --> 00:01:54,239
♪ I'M GOING WHERE MY HEART
WILL TAKE ME ♪

13
00:01:54,239 --> 00:01:58,911
♪ I'VE GOT FAITH TO BELIEVE ♪

14
00:01:58,911 --> 00:02:01,956
♪ I CAN DO ANYTHING ♪

15
00:02:01,956 --> 00:02:06,460
♪ I'VE GOT STRENGTH
OF THE SOUL ♪

16
00:02:06,460 --> 00:02:09,588
♪ AND NO ONE'S GONNA BEND
OR BREAK ME ♪

17
00:02:09,588 --> 00:02:14,009
♪ I CAN REACH ANY STAR ♪

18
00:02:15,260 --> 00:02:17,096
♪ I'VE GOT FAITH ♪

19
00:02:17,096 --> 00:02:19,180
♪ I'VE GOT, I'VE GOT, I'VE GOT ♪

20
00:02:19,180 --> 00:02:23,102
♪ I'VE GOT FAITH ♪

21
00:02:23,102 --> 00:02:27,230
♪ FAITH OF THE HEART ♪

22
00:02:37,282 --> 00:02:39,785
ADMIRAL MAXWELL FORREST'S
PERSONAL LOG.

23
00:02:39,785 --> 00:02:41,244
I'VE ARRIVED ON VULCAN

24
00:02:41,244 --> 00:02:43,371
HOPEFUL THAT THE HIGH COMMAND
IS FINALLY READY

25
00:02:43,371 --> 00:02:45,833
TO CONDUCT JOINT MISSIONS
WITH STARFLEET.

26
00:02:45,833 --> 00:02:47,876
ADMIRAL,
THE HIGH COMMAND WILL TELL YOU

27
00:02:47,876 --> 00:02:49,837
ITS DECISION AT THE PROPER TIME.

28
00:02:49,837 --> 00:02:51,296
AFTER ALL WE'VE BEEN THROUGH,

29
00:02:51,296 --> 00:02:53,632
I'D RATHER HEAR
THE GOOD NEWS FROM YOU.

30
00:02:53,632 --> 00:02:57,136
THE HIGH COMMAND HASN'T INCLUDED
ME IN THEIR DISCUSSIONS.

31
00:02:57,136 --> 00:02:59,346
THEY'RE NOT TELLING
THEIR OWN AMBASSADOR TO EARTH

32
00:02:59,346 --> 00:03:01,306
WHAT THEY'RE PLANNING?

33
00:03:01,306 --> 00:03:02,975
WELCOME TO THE CLUB.

34
00:03:02,975 --> 00:03:05,644
ADMIRAL,
I KNOW YOU FIND OUR RELUCTANCE

35
00:03:05,644 --> 00:03:08,313
TO SHARE TECHNOLOGY
AND DISCOVERIES RESTRICTIVE.

36
00:03:08,313 --> 00:03:12,400
I CAN THINK OF
A FEW STRONGER WORDS THAN THAT.

37
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:15,654
WE DON'T KNOW
WHAT TO DO ABOUT HUMANS.

38
00:03:15,654 --> 00:03:18,073
OF ALL THE SPECIES
WE'VE MADE CONTACT WITH,

39
00:03:18,073 --> 00:03:20,826
YOURS IS THE ONLY ONE
WE CAN'T DEFINE.

40
00:03:20,826 --> 00:03:23,078
YOU HAVE
THE ARROGANCE OF ANDORIANS,

41
00:03:23,078 --> 00:03:25,039
THE STUBBORN PRIDE
OF TELLARITES.

42
00:03:25,039 --> 00:03:28,291
ONE MOMENT YOU'RE AS DRIVEN
BY YOUR EMOTIONS AS KLINGONS,

43
00:03:28,291 --> 00:03:32,295
AND THE NEXT, YOU CONFOUND US
BY SUDDENLY EMBRACING LOGIC.

44
00:03:32,295 --> 00:03:33,547
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

45
00:03:33,547 --> 00:03:35,174
[ BEEPING ]

46
00:03:35,174 --> 00:03:37,634
I'M SURE THOSE QUALITIES
ARE FOUND IN EVERY SPECIES.

47
00:03:37,634 --> 00:03:40,054
NOT IN SUCH CONFUSING ABUNDANCE.

48
00:03:40,054 --> 00:03:43,682
NEXT, PLEASE.
STEP UP TO THE SCANNER.

49
00:03:43,682 --> 00:03:45,184
AMBASSADOR...

50
00:03:47,769 --> 00:03:49,980
...ARE VULCANS AFRAID OF HUMANS?

51
00:03:53,150 --> 00:03:55,069
WHY?

52
00:03:55,069 --> 00:03:57,738
BECAUSE THERE IS ONE SPECIES
YOU REMIND US OF.

53
00:03:59,990 --> 00:04:02,450
VULCANS.

54
00:04:02,450 --> 00:04:05,412
WE HAD OUR WARS, ADMIRAL.
JUST AS HUMANS DID.

55
00:04:05,412 --> 00:04:06,830
OUR PLANET WAS DEVASTATED,

56
00:04:06,830 --> 00:04:08,999
OUR CIVILIZATION
NEARLY DESTROYED.

57
00:04:08,999 --> 00:04:10,876
LOGIC SAVED US.

58
00:04:10,876 --> 00:04:13,461
BUT IT TOOK ALMOST 1,500 YEARS

59
00:04:13,461 --> 00:04:15,964
FOR US TO REBUILD OUR WORLD
AND TRAVEL TO THE STARS.

60
00:04:15,964 --> 00:04:19,426
YOU HUMANS DID THE SAME
IN LESS THAN A CENTURY.

61
00:04:21,302 --> 00:04:23,889
THERE ARE THOSE
ON THE HIGH COMMAND

62
00:04:23,889 --> 00:04:27,184
WHO WONDER
WHAT HUMANS WOULD ACHIEVE

63
00:04:27,184 --> 00:04:29,310
IN THE CENTURY TO COME.

64
00:04:29,310 --> 00:04:32,064
AND THEY DON'T LIKE THE ANSWER.

65
00:04:32,064 --> 00:04:35,109
WE'RE NOT THE KLINGONS.

66
00:04:35,109 --> 00:04:37,569
WE ONLY WANT TO BE
YOUR PARTNERS,

67
00:04:37,569 --> 00:04:41,240
TO DO WHAT THE NATIONS OF EARTH
HAVE LEARNED TO DO --

68
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:43,242
TO WORK TOGETHER
IN COMMON CAUSE.

69
00:04:43,242 --> 00:04:47,204
UNFORTUNATELY, THE FUTURE
OF RELATIONS BETWEEN OUR WORLDS

70
00:04:47,204 --> 00:04:48,872
IS NOT MINE TO CONTROL.

71
00:04:48,872 --> 00:04:50,331
[ EXPLOSION ]

72
00:05:04,930 --> 00:05:06,098
CAPTAIN!

73
00:05:07,933 --> 00:05:10,852
HERE!

74
00:05:10,852 --> 00:05:12,604
[ GRUNTING ]

75
00:05:12,604 --> 00:05:13,897
AH.

76
00:05:13,897 --> 00:05:15,565
-[ LAUGHING ]
-OH!

77
00:05:15,565 --> 00:05:18,777
-THAT'S ANOTHER GAME -- 21-TO-2.
-[ LAUGHS ]

78
00:05:18,777 --> 00:05:21,071
TIME TO SWITCH SIDES AGAIN,
DOCTOR.

79
00:05:21,071 --> 00:05:23,031
CERTAINLY.

80
00:05:23,031 --> 00:05:25,159
THIS IS A MOST ENJOYABLE SPORT,

81
00:05:25,159 --> 00:05:27,161
REMINISCENT
OF OCTRAN FERTILITY CONTESTS.

82
00:05:27,161 --> 00:05:28,536
-[ DOOR OPENS ]
-OH, GOOD.

83
00:05:28,536 --> 00:05:30,747
[ LAUGHTER ]

84
00:05:30,747 --> 00:05:34,876
CAPTAIN...I'VE JUST SPOKEN
WITH STARFLEET COMMAND.

85
00:05:34,876 --> 00:05:36,878
EXCEPT WE'RE, UH, FULLY CLOTHED,

86
00:05:36,878 --> 00:05:39,506
[ CHUCKLES ]
WHICH IS PROBABLY FOR THE BEST.

87
00:05:48,140 --> 00:05:50,225
CAPTAIN'S STARLOG, SUPPLEMENTAL.

88
00:05:50,225 --> 00:05:53,187
<i>ENTERPRISE</i> HAS ARRIVED
AT VULCAN AS ORDERED.

89
00:05:53,187 --> 00:05:55,856
THREE DAYS AFTER THE BOMBING
OF EARTH'S EMBASSY,

90
00:05:55,856 --> 00:05:58,566
THE DEATH TOLL STANDS AT 43,

91
00:05:58,566 --> 00:06:01,402
AND I HAVE LOST MY FRIEND
ADMIRAL FORREST.

92
00:06:01,402 --> 00:06:04,323
VULCAN AUTHORITIES STILL HAVE
NO LEAD ON WHO'S RESPONSIBLE.

93
00:06:04,323 --> 00:06:06,074
I'M SORRY TO KEEP YOU
FROM YOUR FAMILY,

94
00:06:06,074 --> 00:06:08,409
BUT I'M GONNA NEED YOU
ON THE INVESTIGATION FULL TIME.

95
00:06:08,409 --> 00:06:10,745
THAT'S WHERE I PREFER TO BE.

96
00:06:10,745 --> 00:06:15,292
YOUR MOTHER AND HUSBAND
WILL UNDERSTAND?

97
00:06:15,292 --> 00:06:18,377
MY MOTHER HASN'T RESPONDED
TO MY COMMUNIQUéS.

98
00:06:18,377 --> 00:06:21,589
IT'S NOT UNUSUAL FOR HER
TO BECOME LOST IN HER WORK.

99
00:06:21,589 --> 00:06:23,550
AS FOR MY...HUSBAND,

100
00:06:23,550 --> 00:06:26,803
OUR ARRANGEMENT REMAINS
UNCHANGED.

101
00:06:32,517 --> 00:06:34,602
CAPTAIN JONATHAN ARCHER.

102
00:06:34,602 --> 00:06:36,980
I REGRET WE MEET UNDER
SUCH TRAGIC CIRCUMSTANCES.

103
00:06:36,980 --> 00:06:41,109
I'D LIKE TO INTRODUCE
ADMINISTRATOR V'LAS.

104
00:06:41,109 --> 00:06:43,195
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

105
00:06:43,195 --> 00:06:45,239
ADMINISTRATOR.

106
00:06:45,239 --> 00:06:47,908
I WASN'T TOLD TO EXPECT
THE HEAD OF THE HIGH COMMAND.

107
00:06:47,908 --> 00:06:51,245
CAPTAIN ARCHER, ALL OF VULCAN
GRIEVES WITH YOU TODAY.

108
00:06:52,746 --> 00:06:55,165
12 VULCANS DIED IN THE BLAST,
AMBASSADOR.

109
00:06:55,165 --> 00:06:56,708
TO THAT END, THIS IS STEL,

110
00:06:56,708 --> 00:06:59,627
CHIEF INVESTIGATOR
OF OUR SECURITY DIRECTORATE.

111
00:06:59,627 --> 00:07:02,547
CAPTAIN, WE NOW HAVE SUSPECTS.

112
00:07:06,301 --> 00:07:09,388
ANDORIANS?

113
00:07:09,388 --> 00:07:11,139
WHY WOULD THEY ATTACK
OUR EMBASSY?

114
00:07:11,139 --> 00:07:14,142
TO CREATE CONFLICT
BETWEEN EARTH AND VULCAN.

115
00:07:14,142 --> 00:07:17,729
THEY DO CONSIDER US ALLIES
WHO STAND AGAINST THEM.

116
00:07:17,729 --> 00:07:20,732
SO FAR, WE'VE DONE OUR BEST
TO REMAIN NEUTRAL,

117
00:07:20,732 --> 00:07:22,650
AND THE ANDORIANS KNOW THAT.

118
00:07:22,650 --> 00:07:24,736
THEY HAVE NOTHING TO GAIN
BY ATTACKING US.

119
00:07:27,114 --> 00:07:28,990
YOU HAVE OTHER SUSPECTS?

120
00:07:30,325 --> 00:07:31,451
SYRRANNITES.

121
00:07:31,451 --> 00:07:33,661
I'VE NEVER HEARD
OF THAT SPECIES.

122
00:07:33,661 --> 00:07:37,082
ACTUALLY, THEY'RE
A SMALL GROUP OF VULCANS.

123
00:07:37,082 --> 00:07:41,211
THEY FOLLOW A CORRUPTED FORM
OF SURAK'S TEACHINGS.

124
00:07:41,211 --> 00:07:44,547
SURAK I'VE HEARD OF.

125
00:07:44,547 --> 00:07:46,300
HE'S THE FATHER OF VULCAN LOGIC.

126
00:07:46,300 --> 00:07:48,676
EVEN AFTER 1,800 YEARS,
WE CONSIDER HIM

127
00:07:48,676 --> 00:07:51,179
THE MOST IMPORTANT VULCAN
WHO EVER LIVED.

128
00:07:51,179 --> 00:07:54,182
SO WHY WOULD THESE SYRRANNITES
WANT TO ATTACK OUR EMBASSY?

129
00:07:54,182 --> 00:07:55,934
IT'S HARDLY AN ACT OF LOGIC.

130
00:07:55,934 --> 00:07:58,812
THEY'VE BEEN VOCAL ABOUT
THEIR OPPOSITION TO GOVERNMENT,

131
00:07:58,812 --> 00:08:00,439
BUT ALWAYS PEACEFUL.

132
00:08:00,439 --> 00:08:01,731
OVER THE PAST YEAR,

133
00:08:01,731 --> 00:08:03,984
THEIR LEADER,
A DISSIDENT NAMED SYRRAN,

134
00:08:03,984 --> 00:08:05,568
HAS BECOME A DANGEROUS ZEALOT.

135
00:08:05,568 --> 00:08:07,654
CAPTAIN...

136
00:08:07,654 --> 00:08:09,323
I TRUST YOU TO KEEP
THIS MATTER CONFIDENTIAL.

137
00:08:09,323 --> 00:08:12,033
WE DON'T SHARE IT LIGHTLY.

138
00:08:12,033 --> 00:08:14,077
BUT RECENTLY, ON OUR WORLD,

139
00:08:14,077 --> 00:08:17,705
THERE HAVE BEEN INSTANCES
OF VIOLENCE AGAINST NON-VULCANS.

140
00:08:17,705 --> 00:08:19,374
THOUGH WE HAVE
NO CONCLUSIVE PROOF,

141
00:08:19,374 --> 00:08:24,879
THERE ARE SIGNS THAT SYRRANNITES
MIGHT BE RESPONSIBLE.

142
00:08:24,879 --> 00:08:26,173
IS THERE ANY EVIDENCE

143
00:08:26,173 --> 00:08:29,926
CONNECTING SYRRANITES
TO THE BOMBING?

144
00:08:29,926 --> 00:08:34,889
YOUR EMBASSY IS OFFICIALLY
CONSIDERED TO BE ON EARTH SOIL.

145
00:08:34,889 --> 00:08:37,476
WE'VE PRESERVED THE SITE
FOR YOU TO INVESTIGATE.

146
00:08:37,476 --> 00:08:39,269
IF EVIDENCE IS THERE,

147
00:08:39,269 --> 00:08:42,147
THE CHIEF INVESTIGATOR AND I
FEEL CONFIDENT YOU'LL FIND IT.

148
00:08:42,147 --> 00:08:44,316
I INTEND TO.

149
00:08:47,735 --> 00:08:51,572
LIEUTENANT,
HERE'S THE JUNCTION ROOM.

150
00:09:16,973 --> 00:09:18,517
[ GRUNTING ]

151
00:09:18,517 --> 00:09:20,018
SCHEMATICS SAY

152
00:09:20,018 --> 00:09:22,479
THE SECONDARY SECURITY BANK'S
RIGHT IN THERE.

153
00:09:22,479 --> 00:09:24,439
[ GRUNTS ]

154
00:09:24,439 --> 00:09:26,733
STILL IN ONE PIECE.

155
00:09:30,904 --> 00:09:33,365
THERE'S A WEAK POWER SIGNATURE
UNDER THIS MESS.

156
00:09:33,365 --> 00:09:36,159
IT'S PROBABLY
AN EMERGENCY LIGHT...

157
00:09:36,159 --> 00:09:38,203
RUNNING ON BATTERIES.

158
00:09:40,330 --> 00:09:41,956
[ BEEPING ]

159
00:09:41,956 --> 00:09:44,000
WELL, THERE'S SOMETHING HERE --

160
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:46,127
SOME KIND
OF SURVEILLANCE RECORDER.

161
00:09:46,127 --> 00:09:48,213
[ GRUNTING ]

162
00:09:53,510 --> 00:09:54,886
LIEUTENANT.

163
00:09:58,390 --> 00:10:01,101
THE TIMER MIGHT BE BROKEN,
BUT THAT BOMB'S ARMED.

164
00:10:01,101 --> 00:10:02,477
DON'T MOVE.

165
00:10:02,477 --> 00:10:05,522
THE SLIGHTEST VIBRATION
MIGHT SET IT OFF.

166
00:10:09,817 --> 00:10:10,860
[ BEEPS ]

167
00:10:10,860 --> 00:10:12,987
REED TO<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

168
00:10:12,987 --> 00:10:16,116
I NEED
AN EMERGENCY TRANSPORTER LOCK.

169
00:10:16,116 --> 00:10:17,825
TWO TO BEAM UP ON MY MARK.

170
00:10:17,825 --> 00:10:19,660
Acknowledged.

171
00:10:22,330 --> 00:10:23,790
WHY NOT BEAM THE BOMB
OUT OF HERE.

172
00:10:23,790 --> 00:10:25,208
IF THERE'S A GRAVITY SWITCH,

173
00:10:25,208 --> 00:10:27,419
IT'LL DETONATE
IN THE MATTER STREAM.

174
00:10:27,419 --> 00:10:29,796
<i>Enterprise</i> to Reed.
The transporter's locked.

175
00:10:29,796 --> 00:10:31,839
Do you need assistance?

176
00:10:31,839 --> 00:10:34,926
NEGATIVE,<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>
<i>STAND BY.</i>

177
00:10:37,637 --> 00:10:39,431
I'M GOING TO ATTEMPT TO SCAN IT.

178
00:10:39,431 --> 00:10:40,848
ATTEMPT?

179
00:10:40,848 --> 00:10:42,225
YEAH.

180
00:10:42,225 --> 00:10:44,603
IF I'D DESIGNED THAT BOMB,

181
00:10:44,603 --> 00:10:49,274
I'D RIG IT TO GO OFF THE INSTANT
A SENSOR BEAM MADE CONTACT.

182
00:10:51,901 --> 00:10:54,279
LOOK ON THE BRIGHT SIDE --

183
00:10:54,279 --> 00:10:56,990
IF IT DETONATES...

184
00:10:56,990 --> 00:10:58,366
WE'LL NEVER KNOW.

185
00:10:59,909 --> 00:11:01,202
STEADY.

186
00:11:01,202 --> 00:11:03,079
[ THUDDING ]

187
00:11:09,586 --> 00:11:11,546
[ BEEPING ]

188
00:11:13,714 --> 00:11:16,884
[ SIGHING ]

189
00:11:16,884 --> 00:11:20,763
THERE'S VULCAN DNA
ON THESE CONTROLS.

190
00:11:20,763 --> 00:11:24,643
SO MUCH FOR BLAMING ANDORIANS.

191
00:11:24,643 --> 00:11:27,020
TESTING SCAN RESOLUTION.

192
00:11:27,020 --> 00:11:29,356
[ BEEPING ]

193
00:11:29,356 --> 00:11:30,689
THAT CAN'T BE GOOD.

194
00:11:30,689 --> 00:11:32,066
OH, DAMN.

195
00:11:32,066 --> 00:11:33,985
<i>ENTERPRISE,</i> MARK.

196
00:11:33,985 --> 00:11:35,987
[ BEEPING RAPIDLY ]

197
00:11:37,280 --> 00:11:39,449
<i>ENTERPRISE!</i>

198
00:11:47,457 --> 00:11:49,584
ACCORDING TO
THE VULCAN GENOME REGISTRY,

199
00:11:49,584 --> 00:11:54,631
THE DNA ON THE BOMB'S CONTROLS
WAS LEFT BY THIS WOMAN, T'PAU.

200
00:11:54,631 --> 00:11:56,007
SINCE YOU HAD HER DNA ON RECORD,

201
00:11:56,007 --> 00:11:57,634
DOES THAT MEAN
SHE'S BEEN ARRESTED BEFORE?

202
00:11:57,634 --> 00:12:01,513
THE REGISTRY RECORDS DNA
FROM ALL VULCANS AT BIRTH.

203
00:12:01,513 --> 00:12:02,763
DO YOU KNOW ANYTHING ABOUT HER?

204
00:12:02,763 --> 00:12:04,765
T'PAU IS
A WELL-KNOWN SYRRANNITE.

205
00:12:06,267 --> 00:12:07,935
ALL RIGHT.

206
00:12:07,935 --> 00:12:10,104
WE'VE GOT A SOLID START.

207
00:12:10,104 --> 00:12:11,606
NOW WE NEED TO FIND HER.

208
00:12:11,606 --> 00:12:15,068
CAPTAIN, T'PAU IS VULCAN.

209
00:12:15,068 --> 00:12:16,986
THE SECURITY DIRECTORATE
WILL TAKE CHARGE

210
00:12:16,986 --> 00:12:18,572
OF THE INVESTIGATION.

211
00:12:18,572 --> 00:12:21,782
OF COURSE.
VULCAN SOVEREIGNTY.

212
00:12:21,782 --> 00:12:23,368
LIEUTENANT REED
AND COMMANDER T'POL

213
00:12:23,368 --> 00:12:24,994
WILL WORK WITH YOU.

214
00:12:24,994 --> 00:12:27,872
THEIR ASSISTANCE ISN'T REQUIRED.

215
00:12:29,207 --> 00:12:31,585
CHIEF INVESTIGATOR,

216
00:12:31,585 --> 00:12:34,212
43 PEOPLE DIED IN THE BOMBING.

217
00:12:34,212 --> 00:12:36,755
12 VULCANS AND 31 HUMANS.

218
00:12:36,755 --> 00:12:38,258
WE WANT HER AS MUCH AS YOU DO.

219
00:12:38,258 --> 00:12:41,928
THIS IS NOW
A VULCAN SECURITY OPERATION.

220
00:12:41,928 --> 00:12:43,638
WE'LL INFORM AMBASSADOR SOVAL

221
00:12:43,638 --> 00:12:45,890
OF ANY DEVELOPMENTS
THAT CONCERN YOU.

222
00:13:30,393 --> 00:13:32,604
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

223
00:13:37,066 --> 00:13:40,654
HIS DEATH IS A LOSS
TO BOTH OUR WORLDS.

224
00:13:40,654 --> 00:13:42,322
IF YOU'RE LOST, AMBASSADOR,

225
00:13:42,322 --> 00:13:44,699
I CAN DIRECT YOU
TO YOUR SHUTTLE.

226
00:13:48,703 --> 00:13:53,374
HE SAVED MY LIFE...
IN THE EXPLOSION.

227
00:13:56,043 --> 00:13:59,005
HE COULD HAVE SAVED HIMSELF.

228
00:14:06,012 --> 00:14:11,476
HE ALWAYS PUT...
THE MISSION FIRST.

229
00:14:16,523 --> 00:14:18,232
THE LAST TIME WE SPOKE,

230
00:14:18,232 --> 00:14:23,029
HE WAS ANTICIPATING THE PROSPECT
OF JOINT MISSIONS...

231
00:14:24,238 --> 00:14:27,408
...HUMANS AND VULCANS
WORKING TOGETHER.

