462
00:27:59,719 --> 00:28:02,473
THOSE WHO DO HAVE THE ABILITY
WON'T RISK THEIR CAREERS

463
00:28:02,473 --> 00:28:04,766
BY PUBLICLY ATTEMPTING
WHAT YOU SUGGEST.

464
00:28:04,766 --> 00:28:08,604
MOST VULCANS SEE MELDING
AS DEVIANT BEHAVIOR.

465
00:28:08,604 --> 00:28:09,813
WHAT'S THAT GOT TO DO WITH IT?

466
00:28:09,813 --> 00:28:11,273
[ SIGHS ]

467
00:28:11,273 --> 00:28:15,235
EVIDENCE WILL SOLVE THIS CRIME,
NOT MIND-MELDS.

468
00:28:15,235 --> 00:28:16,820
WHAT EVIDENCE?

469
00:28:16,820 --> 00:28:19,573
THE DNA ON THE BOMB WAS PLANTED.

470
00:28:21,074 --> 00:28:22,242
YOU CAN PROVE THAT?

471
00:28:22,242 --> 00:28:23,410
I CAN.

472
00:28:23,410 --> 00:28:24,578
AMBASSADOR...

473
00:28:25,829 --> 00:28:27,247
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT KIND OF POLITICS

474
00:28:27,247 --> 00:28:29,333
TO MESS WITH DNA RECORDS
ON VULCAN,

475
00:28:29,333 --> 00:28:31,210
BUT I THINK WE'RE LOOKING
AT A DELIBERATE ATTEMPT

476
00:28:31,210 --> 00:28:32,628
TO HIDE THE TRUTH.

477
00:28:32,628 --> 00:28:35,506
YOU'RE SUGGESTING A CONSPIRACY.

478
00:28:35,506 --> 00:28:38,592
ONE THAT COST 43 INNOCENT LIVES.

479
00:28:38,592 --> 00:28:40,802
AREN'T THEY WORTH A LITTLE RISK?

480
00:28:43,930 --> 00:28:46,266
THE NEEDS OF THE MANY.

481
00:28:47,767 --> 00:28:51,522
[ SIGHS ]
I CAN PERFORM THE MELD.

482
00:28:57,069 --> 00:28:58,529
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLING ]

483
00:28:58,529 --> 00:29:00,447
[ PANTING ]

484
00:29:01,740 --> 00:29:03,867
[ PANTING ]

485
00:29:12,710 --> 00:29:14,545
[ GRUNTING ]

486
00:29:14,545 --> 00:29:16,380
CAPTAIN.

487
00:29:16,380 --> 00:29:18,465
OVER HERE!

488
00:29:42,906 --> 00:29:44,742
HELP ME WITH THIS.

489
00:29:44,742 --> 00:29:47,620
THE SANDFIRE CAN STILL REACH US.

490
00:29:47,620 --> 00:29:49,705
[ GRUNTING ]

491
00:29:49,705 --> 00:29:51,790
[ CRACKLING CONTINUES ]

492
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:56,086
[ GRUNTING ]

493
00:30:09,725 --> 00:30:11,226
I KNOW THIS.

494
00:30:12,436 --> 00:30:14,062
HOW DID YOU GET THIS MEDALLION?

495
00:30:14,062 --> 00:30:15,814
FROM MY MOTHER.

496
00:30:15,814 --> 00:30:17,608
T'LES.

497
00:30:19,443 --> 00:30:21,069
YOU'RE A SYRRANNITE.

498
00:30:21,069 --> 00:30:23,822
THE DAUGHTER OF T'LES
SERVES ON A HUMAN STARSHIP.

499
00:30:23,822 --> 00:30:27,284
WHEN DID YOU TALK WITH HER?
IS SHE SAFE?

500
00:30:30,162 --> 00:30:31,705
YOU'RE THE HUMAN RESPONSIBLE

501
00:30:31,705 --> 00:30:34,207
FOR THE DESTRUCTION
OF THE MONASTERY AT P'JEM.

502
00:30:35,542 --> 00:30:37,336
IS THAT GONNA BE A PROBLEM?

503
00:30:37,336 --> 00:30:38,754
THE HIGH COMMAND DEFILED P'JEM

504
00:30:38,754 --> 00:30:41,840
WHEN THEY USED IT
TO SPY ON ANDORIA.

505
00:30:41,840 --> 00:30:43,592
YOU EXPOSED THEIR HYPOCRISY.

506
00:30:43,592 --> 00:30:46,261
YOU SEEM TO KNOW A LOT ABOUT US.

507
00:30:46,261 --> 00:30:49,848
I'M GUESSING THAT MEANS
YOU KNOW WHY WE'RE HERE.

508
00:30:49,848 --> 00:30:51,891
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLING ]

509
00:30:53,101 --> 00:30:54,853
YOUR MOTHER IS SAFE
WITH THE OTHERS,

510
00:30:54,853 --> 00:30:56,396
AT THE T'KARATH SANCTUARY.

511
00:30:56,396 --> 00:30:59,107
IT'S NOT FAR.

512
00:30:59,107 --> 00:31:01,401
I'LL GUIDE YOU BOTH THERE
WHEN THE STORM HAS PASSED.

513
00:31:09,326 --> 00:31:10,952
I DON'T KNOW

514
00:31:10,952 --> 00:31:14,331
IF THIS HAS EVER BEEN ATTEMPTED
WITH A HUMAN BEFORE.

515
00:31:30,013 --> 00:31:32,850
[ SIGHING ]

516
00:31:32,850 --> 00:31:35,935
MY MIND...TO YOUR MIND.

517
00:31:38,188 --> 00:31:40,566
OUR MINDS ARE ONE.

518
00:31:40,566 --> 00:31:43,443
OUR THOUGHTS ARE JOINED.

519
00:31:50,576 --> 00:31:53,036
YES.

520
00:31:53,036 --> 00:31:55,748
I SEE WHAT YOU SEE...

521
00:31:56,874 --> 00:31:59,125
...THE EMBASSY.

522
00:32:00,419 --> 00:32:03,171
I'M AT MY STATION...

523
00:32:03,171 --> 00:32:05,465
AT<i> YOUR</i> STATION.

524
00:32:08,093 --> 00:32:13,640
SO MANY NEW PEOPLE ARRIVING
FOR THE SUMMIT.

525
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:15,642
I DON'T RECOGNIZE THEM ALL...

526
00:32:16,769 --> 00:32:19,938
...BUT SOME I KNOW.

527
00:32:28,154 --> 00:32:30,240
A PACKAGE.

528
00:32:30,240 --> 00:32:32,284
THAT'S ALL RIGHT.

529
00:32:32,284 --> 00:32:35,287
I DON'T NEED TO SEE IT.
GO RIGHT THROUGH.

530
00:32:38,164 --> 00:32:40,584
WHO ARE YOU?

531
00:32:40,584 --> 00:32:43,044
WHO?

532
00:32:43,044 --> 00:32:45,714
[ GASPING ]

533
00:32:45,714 --> 00:32:49,426
AMBASSADOR...

534
00:32:49,426 --> 00:32:51,553
WHAT'D YOU SEE?

535
00:32:56,308 --> 00:32:58,351
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLES ]

536
00:33:03,941 --> 00:33:07,736
HOW LONG DO THESE SANDFIRE
STORMS USUALLY LAST?

537
00:33:14,534 --> 00:33:17,245
A DAY...PERHAPS TWO.

538
00:33:17,245 --> 00:33:18,789
I'VE NEVER SEEN ONE THIS STRONG.

539
00:33:18,789 --> 00:33:23,084
BUT WE'RE SAFE HERE,
AND WE'RE IN NO HURRY.

540
00:33:23,084 --> 00:33:25,170
MAYBE WE SHOULD BE.

541
00:33:25,170 --> 00:33:27,506
THE HIGH COMMAND BELIEVES
THE SYRRANNITES ARE RESPONSIBLE

542
00:33:27,506 --> 00:33:29,215
FOR BOMBING THE EARTH EMBASSY.

543
00:33:30,216 --> 00:33:31,802
THAT'S NOT OUR WAY.

544
00:33:31,802 --> 00:33:33,595
THEY SEEM TO THINK THAT IT IS --

545
00:33:33,595 --> 00:33:35,180
THAT YOU AND YOUR LEADER

546
00:33:35,180 --> 00:33:37,474
BELIEVE IN A CORRUPTED VERSION
OF SURAK'S TEACHINGS.

547
00:33:37,474 --> 00:33:39,977
[ CHUCKLING ]

548
00:33:39,977 --> 00:33:41,812
DID YOUR MOTHER TELL YOU
THE STORY?

549
00:33:43,772 --> 00:33:45,315
OF THE IDIC? 

550
00:33:45,315 --> 00:33:49,027
"INFINITE DIVERSITY
IN INFINITE COMBINATION,"

551
00:33:49,027 --> 00:33:52,781
WORDS THAT ARE A MERE SHADOW
OF ITS TRUE MEANING.

552
00:33:56,326 --> 00:34:00,789
SURAK TELLS US THAT THE STORY
OF THE IDIC HAS NO END.

553
00:34:00,789 --> 00:34:04,209
BUT IT BEGINS HERE,
AT MOUNT SELEYA.

554
00:34:04,209 --> 00:34:07,253
SURAK DIED ON MOUNT SELEYA.

555
00:34:07,253 --> 00:34:09,088
HIS BODY, YES.

556
00:34:09,088 --> 00:34:11,132
BUT HIS<i> KATRA</i> WAS SPIRITED AWAY

557
00:34:11,132 --> 00:34:12,759
BEFORE THE LAST BATTLE

558
00:34:12,759 --> 00:34:16,304
AGAINST THOSE WHO MARCHED
BENEATH THE RAPTOR'S WINGS,

559
00:34:16,304 --> 00:34:19,474
THOSE WHO WANTED TO RETURN
TO THE SAVAGE WAYS.

560
00:34:19,474 --> 00:34:21,393
WHAT'S A<i> KATRA?</i>

561
00:34:24,062 --> 00:34:28,066
SYRRANNITES CLAIM IT'S
THE ESSENCE OF A VULCAN MIND,

562
00:34:28,066 --> 00:34:31,069
THAT IT CAN BE TRANSFERRED
FROM THE BODY BEFORE DEATH,

563
00:34:31,069 --> 00:34:33,989
THEN STORED IN SOME MANNER.

564
00:34:33,989 --> 00:34:36,491
SOME SAY SURAK'S<i> KATRA</i> WAS FOUND

565
00:34:36,491 --> 00:34:38,577
AND NOW IS CARRIED
BY A SYRRANNITE,

566
00:34:38,577 --> 00:34:42,121
SO ALL THOSE WHO MELD WITH HIM
MAY TOUCH SURAK'S MIND.

567
00:34:43,248 --> 00:34:45,876
SYRRANNITES CONDUCT
MIND-MELDING?

568
00:34:45,876 --> 00:34:48,169
SURAK TELLS US...

569
00:34:48,169 --> 00:34:51,048
IT IS THE HERITAGE
OF EVERY VULCAN...

570
00:34:52,841 --> 00:34:55,552
EVEN THOSE WHO DON'T BELIEVE
IN THE PRACTICE.

571
00:35:01,140 --> 00:35:02,642
A WITNESS?

572
00:35:02,642 --> 00:35:04,143
THE GUARD RECOGNIZED THE PERSON

573
00:35:04,143 --> 00:35:06,187
WHO BROUGHT IN THE BOMB
WE FOUND IN THE RUBBLE.

574
00:35:06,187 --> 00:35:08,398
THE SYRRANNITE WOMAN, T'PAU.

575
00:35:08,398 --> 00:35:10,149
NO.

576
00:35:13,319 --> 00:35:14,738
IT WAS YOU.

577
00:35:16,448 --> 00:35:19,451
I WOULD LIKE TO INTERROGATE
THIS WITNESS MYSELF.

578
00:35:19,451 --> 00:35:20,994
YOU'RE NOT GETTING
ANYWHERE NEAR HIM.

579
00:35:20,994 --> 00:35:23,371
PERHAPS I COULD SPEAK
WITH THE GUARD.

580
00:35:23,371 --> 00:35:25,665
I'M AFRAID HE'S IN NO CONDITION
TO BE QUESTIONED.

581
00:35:26,792 --> 00:35:29,377
HE'S IN A COMA.

582
00:35:29,377 --> 00:35:35,258
YET, HE PROVIDED
AN EYE-WITNESS ACCOUNT.

583
00:35:35,258 --> 00:35:39,345
WE ACCESSED HIS MEMORIES
THROUGH A MIND-MELD.

584
00:35:41,848 --> 00:35:44,059
TELEPATHIC EVIDENCE
IS INADMISSIBLE.

585
00:35:44,059 --> 00:35:46,394
IT'S NOT EVIDENCE AT ALL!

586
00:35:49,064 --> 00:35:53,485
YOU ALLOWED THIS DISTASTEFUL ACT
TO TAKE PLACE?

587
00:35:53,485 --> 00:35:55,194
I PERFORMED IT.

588
00:35:59,032 --> 00:36:01,159
[ SIGHS ]
SOVAL.

589
00:36:02,661 --> 00:36:07,582
YOU'VE SHAMED VULCAN...
AND YOURSELF.

590
00:36:07,582 --> 00:36:10,376
THE LAW LEAVES ME NO RECOURSE.

591
00:36:10,376 --> 00:36:12,754
YOU'LL BE SUMMONED TO APPEAR
BEFORE THE HIGH COMMAND

592
00:36:12,754 --> 00:36:14,464
TO ACCOUNT FOR YOUR ACTIONS.

593
00:36:16,466 --> 00:36:19,886
COMMANDER. DOCTOR.

594
00:36:22,180 --> 00:36:24,641
AT ONE TIME, THE HIGH COMMAND
WAS ONLY RESPONSIBLE

595
00:36:24,641 --> 00:36:26,893
FOR THE EXPLORATION OF SPACE.

596
00:36:26,893 --> 00:36:28,520
BUT THAT'S CHANGED.

597
00:36:30,605 --> 00:36:33,274
I'VE BEEN TOLD VULCANS
HAVE NEVER BEEN EXPLORERS.

598
00:36:33,274 --> 00:36:34,567
I THINK YOU'VE BEEN TOLD

599
00:36:34,567 --> 00:36:36,153
MANY THINGS ABOUT US
THAT AREN'T TRUE.

600
00:36:36,153 --> 00:36:37,779
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLING ]

601
00:36:40,198 --> 00:36:41,908
RESEAL THE ENTRANCE!

602
00:36:44,077 --> 00:36:45,578
[ GRUNTING ]

603
00:36:47,539 --> 00:36:49,290
AAH!

604
00:36:49,290 --> 00:36:50,792
T'POL!

605
00:36:55,797 --> 00:36:57,883
[ GROANING ]

606
00:36:57,883 --> 00:36:59,718
EASY.

607
00:36:59,718 --> 00:37:00,802
EASY, EASY, EASY.

608
00:37:00,802 --> 00:37:02,054
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLING ]

609
00:37:02,054 --> 00:37:04,890
LISTEN.
THE STORM IS GAINING STRENGTH.

610
00:37:06,432 --> 00:37:08,768
AAH! UGH!

611
00:37:09,811 --> 00:37:12,189
[ GROANING ]

612
00:37:12,189 --> 00:37:13,690
AREV.

613
00:37:15,525 --> 00:37:18,486
YOU MUST CARRY IT TO SANCTUARY.

614
00:37:18,486 --> 00:37:19,738
CARRY WHAT?

615
00:37:20,697 --> 00:37:22,199
[ GROANING ]

616
00:37:22,199 --> 00:37:27,662
-<i> TULUK TU VOKAU.</i>
<i>-[ GRUNTING ]</i>

617
00:37:27,662 --> 00:37:30,082
[ GROANING ]

618
00:37:30,082 --> 00:37:31,208
YOU CAN'T GO BACK.

619
00:37:31,208 --> 00:37:33,043
I'M NOT A FOOL, COMMANDER.

620
00:37:33,043 --> 00:37:35,378
V'LAS WAS INVOLVED
WITH THE ATTACK ON YOUR EMBASSY.

621
00:37:35,378 --> 00:37:37,881
HE'S RESPONSIBLE FOR BLAMING IT
ON THE SYRRANNITES.

622
00:37:37,881 --> 00:37:40,050
THEN WHY TURN YOURSELF OVER
TO HIM?

623
00:37:41,509 --> 00:37:43,178
IT'S THE ONLY CHANCE I'LL HAVE

624
00:37:43,178 --> 00:37:45,180
TO REACH THE REST
OF THE HIGH COMMAND.

625
00:37:45,180 --> 00:37:46,806
WHAT IF THEY'RE ALL IN ON IT?

626
00:37:53,105 --> 00:37:54,981
IF YOU REALLY WANT
HUMANS AND VULCANS

627
00:37:54,981 --> 00:37:56,942
TO WORK TOGETHER SOMEDAY,

628
00:37:56,942 --> 00:37:59,111
YOU MIGHT START THINKING
ABOUT TRUSTING US.

629
00:38:03,531 --> 00:38:06,409
PEACE AND LONG LIFE, COMMANDER.

630
00:38:06,409 --> 00:38:07,869
[ BEEPS ]

631
00:38:10,122 --> 00:38:11,998
RIGHT.

632
00:38:14,500 --> 00:38:16,711
[ SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY ]

633
00:38:26,054 --> 00:38:28,556
AREV.

634
00:38:34,604 --> 00:38:36,815
[ GROANS ]

635
00:38:36,815 --> 00:38:38,858
[ GROANING ]

636
00:38:38,858 --> 00:38:39,985
ARE YOU INJURED?

637
00:38:39,985 --> 00:38:41,486
I'M FINE.

638
00:38:43,196 --> 00:38:47,033
HE...SAID SOMETHING IN VULCAN --

639
00:38:47,033 --> 00:38:48,451
<i>"VOKAU."</i>

640
00:38:48,451 --> 00:38:50,495
"REMEMBER."

641
00:38:50,495 --> 00:38:52,413
REMEMBER WHAT?

642
00:38:53,832 --> 00:38:58,962
I THINK HE -- HE PUNCHED ME.

643
00:39:00,213 --> 00:39:02,007
OHH.

644
00:39:02,007 --> 00:39:04,009
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

645
00:39:04,009 --> 00:39:05,551
THE STORM'S OVER?

646
00:39:05,551 --> 00:39:07,720
[ ENGINE HUMMING ]

647
00:39:09,472 --> 00:39:11,099
THE PATROL CRAFT
ARE FLYING AGAIN.

648
00:39:11,099 --> 00:39:13,643
THEY SOUND LIKE THEY'RE
CLOSING IN ON THIS LOCATION.

649
00:39:16,354 --> 00:39:20,192
HE SAID WE WEREN'T FAR
FROM THE T'KARATH SANCTUARY.

650
00:39:20,192 --> 00:39:22,443
WE SHOULD KEEP MOVING.

651
00:39:25,738 --> 00:39:28,200
AFTER WE BURY HIM.

652
00:39:40,337 --> 00:39:44,174
[ ENGINE HUMMING ]

653
00:39:51,472 --> 00:39:54,726
THEY'RE FOLLOWING
A GRID SEARCH PATTERN.

654
00:39:54,726 --> 00:39:59,314
NO SENSORS, BUT THEY CAN
STILL MAKE VISUAL CONTACT.

655
00:39:59,314 --> 00:40:02,400
WE HAVE TO FIND COVER
BEFORE THE SUN COMES UP.

656
00:40:06,738 --> 00:40:08,823
THAT WAY.

657
00:40:10,867 --> 00:40:12,160
THERE'S NOTHING THERE.

658
00:40:12,160 --> 00:40:14,704
THAT'S WHERE
THE SYRRANNITES ARE.

659
00:40:15,872 --> 00:40:17,749
HOW DO YOU KNOW?

660
00:40:43,691 --> 00:40:45,110
I'M GOOD FOR A FEW MORE DAYS.

661
00:40:45,110 --> 00:40:48,196
CAPTAIN...YOU'RE NOT VULCAN.

662
00:40:51,991 --> 00:40:53,492
RIGHT.

663
00:40:55,453 --> 00:40:57,080
-[ WATER SLOSHES ]
-IT'S ALMOST DAWN.

664
00:40:58,539 --> 00:41:00,875
WE NEED TO FIND
SOMEPLACE TO HIDE.

665
00:41:00,875 --> 00:41:02,877
NO.

666
00:41:02,877 --> 00:41:04,379
OVER HERE.

667
00:41:08,674 --> 00:41:10,551
THAT WON'T HELP US.

668
00:41:14,306 --> 00:41:16,224
[ ENGINE HUMMING ]

669
00:41:28,569 --> 00:41:30,529
DON'T RESIST.

670
00:41:32,157 --> 00:41:33,616
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

671
00:41:39,122 --> 00:41:40,665
[ GRUNTING ]
